				<div id="post-130" class="hentry p4 post publish author-canuckaholic category-graphic-design category-web-design tag-graphic-design-2 tag-image-editing tag-screen-capture is-full comments-open pings-open y2011 m03 d09 h05 alt slug-aviary-suite-of-graphic-tools"><h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://popdigital.ca/2011/03/09/aviary-suite-of-graphic-tools/" title="Permalink to Aviary Suite of Graphic Tools" rel="bookmark">Aviary Suite of Graphic Tools</a></h2>
<div class="entry-meta"><span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">By </span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://popdigital.ca/author/admin/" title="View all posts by Adrian">Adrian</a></span><span class="meta-sep meta-sep-entry-date"> | </span><span class="meta-prep meta-prep-entry-date">Published: </span><span class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2011-03-09T12:46:03-0700">March 9, 2011</abbr></span></div><!-- .entry-meta -->
					<div class="entry-content">
<p><img class="imageFloatRight" title="aviary_website" src="http://popdigital.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/aviary_website.png" alt="" width="250" height="130" />What it is: A free suite of online graphics tools.<br />
Where you can get it: <a title="Aviary" href="http://www.aviary.com/" target="_blank">aviary.com</a></p>
<p>Say good-bye to Photoshop (well, maybe not good-bye forever). With this powerful set of online creation tools all you need is your browser to perform some pretty advanced image editing techniques, screen captures, color editing, and more.</p>
<p>I recommend installing the <a title="Aviary Firefox Extension" href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-us/firefox/addon/aviary-screen-capture-quick-la/" target="_blank">Firefox extension</a>, which allows you to perform a screen capture with the click of a button directly in your browser. It also installs a drop-down menu with quick links to Aviary&#8217;s full suite of tools.</p>
<div class="tweetthis" style="text-align:right;"><p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="tt" href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http://popdigital.ca/2011/03/09/aviary-suite-of-graphic-tools/&text=Aviary+Suite+of+Graphic+Tools&via=tweetthisplugin&related=richardxthripp%2Ctweetthisplugin" title="Post to Twitter"><img class="nothumb" src="http://popdigital.ca/wp-content/plugins/tweet-this/icons/en/twitter/tt-twitter6.png" alt="Post to Twitter" /></a></p></div>
										</div><!-- .entry-content -->
